nodes.text: The 2006 Artoos Awards Ceremony is an article written by Mark Newbold that appeared in Star Wars Insider 90 in 2006. The article covered a Hasbro sponsored event that took place at the bi-annual Memorabila show at Birmingham's National Exhibition Centre.
Newbold submitted the article for inclusion in the Star Wars Insider, and editor Frank Parisi, a recent guest on Newbold's website Lightsabre, published the piece.
